Style FvwmTintBar !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTintBar:*
*FvwmTintBar: Geometry $[vp.width]x28+0-0
*FvwmTintBar: Colorset 28
*FvwmTintBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTintBar: Columns 109
*FvwmTintBar: Frame 1
*FvwmTintBar: Font "xft:Fira Sans:Medium:size=11:antialias=True:hinhstyle=slight"
*FvwmTintBar: (109x1, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) tint2 "Exec exec tint2", Frame 0)

SetEnv DeskHeight 144

Style PagerBlock !Title, BorderWidth 4, HandleWidth 4, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

# FvwmButtons - PagerBlock
#
# FvwmButtons is a powerful module that can be used to build custom
# panels and docks. This config uses FvwmButtons to build the PagerBlock.
# The panel contains buttons to switch desks, FvwmPager, a system tray,
# FvwmIconMan (list of running windows), and a clock.
#
# Note - To use the system tray you must have "stalonetray" installed.
DestroyModuleConfig PagerBlock:*
*PagerBlock: Geometry 144x$[DeskHeight]+2+2
*PagerBlock: Colorset 10
*PagerBlock: Rows $[vp.height]
*PagerBlock: Columns 120
*PagerBlock: Frame 0
*PagerBlock: Font "xft:Sans:Bold:size=10:antialias=True"
*PagerBlock: (30x20, Id desk0, Title "0", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 11, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*PagerBlock: (30x20, Id desk1, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*PagerBlock: (30x20, Id desk2, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*PagerBlock: (30x20, Id desk3, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 0)
*PagerBlock: (120x80, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', Frame 0)

Style TaskPanel !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom

DestroyModuleConfig TaskPanel:*
*TaskPanel: Geometry $[vp.width]x28+0-0
*TaskPanel: Colorset 5
*TaskPanel: Rows 1
*TaskPanel: Columns 20
*TaskPanel: Frame 1
*TaskPanel: Font "xft:Fira Sans:Medium:size=11:antialias=True:hinhstyle=slight"
# *TaskPanel: (2x1, Title "", Icon "$[FVWM_USERDIR]/icons/fvwm-small.png", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file=/home/doug/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc`)
*TaskPanel: (1x1, Title "Fvwm", Icon "", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file="$HOME/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc"`)
*TaskPanel: (16x1, Top, Swallow FvwmIconMan 'Module FvwmIconMan TaskBarIcons', Frame 0)
*TaskPanel: (2x1, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) stalonetray 'Exec exec stalonetray --config "$HOME/.stalonetrayrc"', Frame 0)
*TaskPanel: (1x1, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript $[FVWM_USERDIR]/BarClock', Action Mouse3 `Exec yad --width 360 --class="fbox_cal" --title="Fbox_Calendar" --calendar --text ""`, Frame 1)


